{"tid":832242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現我已經唔識去開展一段新嘅感情","createTime":"2018-09-22T15:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T19:08:24.000Z","uid":66280,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb9efbc842eecf7537ed537699e6ac40d4f070b","tid":832242,"uid":66280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人明依種感受<br />\n讀完大學出到嚟返工<br />\n個生活圈子越嚟越細<br />\n可以識到人嘅機會又少<br />\n身邊識得嘅朋友都冇乜發展空間<br />\n真係難道沒練習太耐 感覺都追不回來<br />\n以前成日聽人講孤獨終老<br />\n心諗呢樣嘢應該唔關我事嘅<br />\n而家個人大左慢慢就覺得自己應該會搭上依條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a677b6a969ea424785c5e7fef0de988a3cd8514c","tid":832242,"uid":67614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"我明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb54381f7682c8254c09e367e406a5adf6cb476","tid":832242,"uid":123122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"我明ar"},{"pid":"16441a9eb8f97569bbbd589da77754032c2770b9","tid":832242,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dd57014022f863e41c471f53071e5bd9c2c47c","tid":832242,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"正是"},{"pid":"4607a8108650f8dd97c86bf1c21c9d1b98797413","tid":832242,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"同感"},{"pid":"e19c198b5fa3f45c96ede031c2fef69dcf011a64","tid":832242,"uid":205101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"明的&hellip;巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692c4e07d86cb07053ce73f508c13ba9e2ee85d7","tid":832242,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:28:03.000Z","msg":"識人當然難<br />\n難就難在識完又要比時間花